      "title": "Temporary Suspension on series of nonessentials",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka has limited imports of 300+ items, including Chocolate and other food preparations containing cocoa, and Perfumes, effective today (23).",
        "The list for the Temporary Suspension of Selected Items includes the following as well;",
        "Stop using PTA, and immediately rescind Detention Orders \u2013 BASL tells President"
